OL,3,CKiller who murdered Radcliffe man and
OL,4,Cthen stole his dog jailed for 19 years
OL,6,FVideo report by ITV Granada's Rob Smith
OL,8,F, has been jailed for a minimum of 19
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FIan Connell, 39, strangled Donald
OL,12,F'Prentice' Patience, 45, in a "fit of
OL,13,Frage" after his victim refused to give
OL,14,Fhim more money to feed his heroin and
OL,15,Fcrack cocaine habit.
OL,17,FThe decomposing body of Mr Patience,
OL,18,Fwas discovered inside a duvet cover at
OL,19,Fthe bottom of his stairs after police
OL,20,Fwere called to reports of a burglary
OL,21,Fat his home in , Greater Manchester.
