OL,6,FA postman dialled 999 on the morning
OL,7,Fof August 22 last year when he saw a
OL,8,Fman climb through the rear kitchen
OL,9,Fwindow of the end terrace property in
OL,10,FAinsworth Road.
OL,12,FWhen police arrived soon afterwards,
OL,13,FConnell was nearby with Mr Patience's
OL,14,Fwhite labradoodle, Layla, on a lead.
OL,16,FConnell lied to officers telling them
OL,17,Fthat the man he described as his "dear
OL,18,Ffriend" was in Scotland and had given
OL,19,Fpermission to break-in and take the
OL,20,Fdog for a walk.
