OL,6,FMr Patience's sister-in-law gave a
OL,7,Fstatement to the court calling him
OL,8,F"one of the kindest and most generous
OL,9,Fpeople." She added there's "a void
OL,10,Fwithin the family that will never be
OL,11,Ffilled" and telling his children of
OL,12,Fhis death was a "conversation you
OL,13,Fshould never have to have."
OL,15,FThe judge at Manchester Crown Court
OL,16,Ftold Connell he'd shown a "temper"
OL,17,Fduring the trial who shook his head
OL,18,Fand snorted during sentencing.
